      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THUNDERING LADY (1) was in the money again last time and not beaten far when second (20.00) at this track in a Other. With a good start should be able to take advantage of the rails draw. Will find this more suitable and can atone. RUSSO (5) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (20.02) last time in a Other at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Has ability and is one of the better chances. KICKER DUSTY (2) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from 10 starts. Below best last time at Murray Bridge Straight (17.45) in a Grade 6, finishing a 2.25 lengths sixth. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. OPTIMISTIC REIGN (7) gave nothing else a chance most recently. Hard to beat again.",
